snippet.title: Scuttle Up - Official Trailer 2025
snippet.description:
Scuttle Up is a new precision platformer (think Only Up!, Chained Together, Getting Over It).

This crab game will you navigating challenging obstacles, collecting hats, and reaching the secret prize at the top. Made with Unreal Engine 5, SU has fully simulated physics, puzzles, compelling environments, and more. 

The trailer pays homage to the amazing anime openings we grew to love (believe it or not, its related to the game)

Wishlist here! - https://store.steampowered.com/app/3124710/Scuttle_Up/
